posts.body:
>Almost nobody in the cake kike's bunker cares 
I think people are (rightfully) eager to be mad at kikewheels, but I find it rather alarming that Mark is being paid by Jim to run /v/. This is exactly the kind of shit that pushed me to come here instead. **Then I realized that most of my posts on /v/ within the past 2-3 years were attempts to get Mark to kill himself and I realize that maybe I don't care about conversing with other people about video games anymore.**

>>ef4aaec1-a4df-4421-808d-b032e874d30a
Well, if something like that comes around, then I suppose it'll be talked about in these channels.

>>e11b994a-9e24-41a4-a215-4f09d589f408
I used to post plenty. After your post gets arbitrarily deleted for the dozenth time, you start to experience some resentment. I realized that the reason most anons on vch are okay with this is because ''Mark is deleting posts that call him out on it.'' That sure pisses in my Cheerios.

>>6ab1f876-13a9-4f31-8f39-4ff0b1601c75
Ah, I think that's fanart of that jewish opera singer with the huge tits. Ben Shapiro's sister or something? Nazis want to fuck her fat kike tits.
While I appreciate your sentiment and taste in clothing, the models in Fallout 4 are way too fucking ugly to be aroused by. And I've jerked off to a lot of Skyrim.

>>cfbf6afc-b832-4494-bc45-ca9604bdfc12
So I guess the plan is to spruce this place up, then?
Become encased in radioactive hellfire, cleansing my sins from this world forevermore.

>>1799b4c8-3deb-46c1-ae3e-9b435bde9a85
You'll have to do that on your own, because social media is fucking garbage, as are the people that use it. Don't bother trying to defend yourself if you actually have a twitter, reddit, or Facebook account, because in that case, your opinion is less than meaningless to me - it is actively subversive. I hate the way most people conduct themselves online and frankly, I don't want fucking anything to do with them because they're the kind of people who drove me off the internet in hte first place/

>>de16bf26-61c7-47e3-9b63-98d4d1653a78
Face it, decentralized imageboards are the only true way forward. Unless some autist gets their shit together and really makes an anoynmous darknet imageboard, any and all imageboards can be targeted and your only hope is to escape to smaller and smaller imageboards or leave the clearnet altogether. Unfortunately, there don't seem to be many of us left here because of the security concerns. I hate talking to people in most channels, so it's vital that we get a truly anonymous decentralized imageboard running so I can tell Mark that his mother caught cancer from giving birth to him without getting banned.

>>740b836e-245a-40b3-a5e0-0a28e5d0aa8b
Yes, and that makes him subhuman. You think I give a fuck? 

>>afe69471-3b77-4eb4-98a3-00c18bfd4caf
If your definition of social media is so broad as to include darknet imageboards, then we're working from different places. If you mean reaching out to other imageboards, then that's different. You'll have to excuse me for feeling like we're in a super sekret klub.

8kun is going to be a flaming morass of garbage, so we should probably get comfy.
